Angeles 65 cloudy; Medford 52 partly cloudy; Pendleton 53 rain;
Phoenix 72 fair; Portland, Ore. 57 cldy; Reno 57 cloudy; Salt Lake
City 61 windy; San Diego 67 partly cloudy; San Francisco 62 cloudy;
